      "subunit": "definite-integrals"
    },
    {
      "id": "di-003",
      "subject": "数学",
      "unit": "calculus-basics",
      "difficulty": "basic",
      "question": "定積分の意味（基本）として正しいものはどれか。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "∫ₐᵇ f(x) dx = F(b)×F(a)"
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "∫ₐᵇ f(x) dx = F'(b)−F'(a)"
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "∫ₐᵇ f(x) dx = F(a)−F(b)"
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "text": "∫ₐᵇ f(x) dx = [F(x)]ₐᵇ = F(b)−F(a) (F は f の原始関数)"
        }
      ],
      "correct": "D",
      "reasoning_tags": [
        "定積分"
      ],
      "subunit": "definite-integrals"
    },
    {
